## Files Modified

1. **`package.json`** (root) — update `pnpm.overrides`, remove `resolutions`
2. **`packages/spotlight/package.json`** — bump `hono` to `^4.12.7`
3. **`pnpm-lock.yaml`** — regenerated by `pnpm install`

