## Verification

After changes:

```bash
# Verify overrides resolved correctly
pnpm why flatted -r      # should show >=3.4.0
pnpm why tar -r           # should show >=7.5.11
pnpm why rollup -r        # should show >=4.59.0
pnpm why hono -r          # should show >=4.12.7
pnpm why devalue -r       # should show >=5.6.4
pnpm why minimatch -r     # no version below thresholds
pnpm why ajv -r           # 6.14.0+ for v6, 8.18.0+ for v8
pnpm why yauzl -r         # v3 copy should be >=3.2.1

# Build check
pnpm build

# Run tests
pnpm test

# Re-check dependabot alerts (may take a few minutes to update after push)
gh api /repos/{owner}/{repo}/dependabot/alerts | jq '[.[] | select(.state == "open")] | length'
```

